AnimationHandler - Class in application
Singleton class which provides a well known access point for all AnimationTimer and Transition There are only 5 public methods available - getInstance - addTransition - addAnimationTimer - start - stop Provide for more functionality to slow down /speed up the rotation / orbital transits As some planet - satellite systems consist of tide-locked objects orbital and rotation scaling should be synchronized
